lead_paragraph: Chanette Hicks had 14 points, seven assists and five steals on Friday night and No. 19 Virginia Tech finished its nonconference season undefeated with an 88-48 win over Delaware State.

headline.print_headline: No. 19 Virginia Tech Beats Delaware State 88-48
